id: "class:bard#busker"
name: "Busker"
description: "A busker uses his dazzling physical stunts to get by on his own in the\
  \ city streets. Buskers commonly use their skills to entertain for a few coins,\
  \ but also pick pockets, hide in plain sight as statues, and manipulate the desperate\
  \ in medicine shows. Many buskers are also jugglers."
